{"tid":2420633,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"未出黎做嘢嘅學生參與政治係愚蠢行為","createTime":"2021-02-24T04:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:27:32.000Z","uid":36383,"like":37,"dislike":155,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"363e88296ea737b748ba4a3d6c1a99d286e5f0dc","tid":2420633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時間會過，人會忘記你地，但最重要係香港價值觀係唔會變，你係社會性死亡<br />\n<br />\n香港，大陸，台灣，新加坡，日本，邊個地區係最拒絕有案底嘅後生仔？係香港<br />\n<br />\n任憑你讀到博士都好，一有案底唔洗諗住香港立足，準備做下躝工。你以為老細/HR 會研究你嘅犯罪時嘅前後因果？No<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">如果你有所覺悟嘅. That's fine. 負皮上一頁，我講嘅嘢唔適用係你身上</span><br />\n<br />\n冇嘅. Don't risk your future. 社會係殘酷，你有案底，身邊嘅大學同學就踩住你 dead body 去 apply MT 呢樣嗰樣<br />\n<br />\n坐完出黎世界都變，好多外國 life boat 政策都會收返，可能連社會評級都唔夠分買機票<br />\n<br />\n同樣嘅說話都講咗好多次，今次係講比大學未畢業又唔甘心嘅大學生聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我預咗比人屌柒，但都係為咗你地前途著想，未畢業不要參與政治活動"},{"pid":"fcaf3bca4b1f7da8411f9ce3473244e4a90f2750","tid":2420633,"uid":34666,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"未畢業係唔係可以唔參加你地臭閪蚑那既蟈情教育呀臭閪蚑那賤蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c69dffa11a3b6524409a8205c9f58794ac5a8ab","tid":2420633,"uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:49:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">請問張六常(欣客)(狗隻#36383)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325823</a>"},{"pid":"546a0cdde86eeffe0769f13dec77d58e39129ab6","tid":2420633,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:01:12.000Z","msg":"三十歲人，有啲生涯劃規經驗想分享畀後生仔女<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2206401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2206401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我講嘅，係基於你地最中意嘅連登巴打評論，超多正皮的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做人核心永遠都係搵錢，搞政治就冇工冇錢"},{"pid":"748a9d52ac20b716b302ee1399072cd7cc7e7871","tid":2420633,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"4c69dffa11a3b6524409a8205c9f58794ac5a8ab","tid":2420633,"uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:49:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">請問張六常(欣客)(狗隻#36383)你屙尿嗰陣起左腳定右腳?</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2325823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2325823</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"做人核心永遠都係搵錢。<br />\n<br />\n二、閣下有咩賣點<br />\n又不妨將自己當成一件商品，你賣點係咩？你係搶手貨定籮底橙？一個人嘅價值，主要由以下條件組成。評估吓自己值幾錢。"},{"pid":"f057f252c7a30f1c73d51a11405d58b530f12650","tid":2420633,"uid":24737,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"黃店waiter好失禮你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n話哂都有最低工資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117a482c593c2b02532ddb697c8c7162b8a8c724","tid":2420633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"fcaf3bca4b1f7da8411f9ce3473244e4a90f2750","tid":2420633,"uid":34666,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T04:48:55.000Z","msg":"未畢業係唔係可以唔參加你地臭閪蚑那既蟈情教育呀臭閪蚑那賤蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"哦，有案底冇工開你養ok?<br />\n唔係你養就咪誤人子弟"},{"pid":"bbb1d4c5f0c62e1dcc08